title: Really!? Chelsea Clinton is (now) VERY concerned about pay-to-play affecting national security
text:
— Alyssa Canobbio (@AlyssaEinDC) February 13, 2017 
Over the weekend there was a report about a discussion Donald Trump may have had with Japan’s Prime Minister: Trump hashed out response to North Korea’s missile launch in the dining room at Mar-a-Lago, eavesdroppers galore https://t.co/t0dkNksx6C 
— Philip Rucker (@PhilipRucker) February 13, 2017 
That got Chelsea Clinton to thinking: How many of Mar-a-Lago's new members will be (already are?) members of foreign intelligence agencies & media organizations? https://t.co/8JqJfoWidP 
— Chelsea Clinton (@ChelseaClinton) February 13, 2017 Trending
